text:
…Does that mean they're complex?
…What happened, all of a sudden?

Um… the other day… the costume staff made me wear these
really, really high-heeled shoes…

I've never worn them before… they were like right angles…!
And then… I couldn't walk at all…

Haha, so that happened, huh…
…What height are "right angle" of heels, I wonder?

Oh… If they're really high,
they could be 15cm or something…!
